"Great news — your match has been confirmed!\n"
"\n"
"Here are your partner's contact details:\n"
"\n"
"Name: %(name)s\n"
"Email: %(email)s\n"
"Phone: %(phone)s\n"
"\n"
"Please get in touch to arrange buying your passes together at the ticket "
"office.\n"
"\n"
"Good luck!"
msgstr ""
"Bonne nouvelle — votre mise en relation est confirmée !\n"
"\n"
"Voici les coordonnées de votre partenaire :\n"
"\n"
"Nom : %(name)s\n"
"E-mail : %(email)s\n"
"Téléphone : %(phone)s\n"
"\n"
"Prenez contact pour organiser l'achat de vos abonnements ensemble au "
"guichet.\n"
"\n"
"Bonne chance !"

#: matching/services.py:877
msgid "Your match has been reported as a no-show"
msgstr "Votre mise en relation a été signalée comme absence"

#: matching/services.py:879
msgid ""
"We have received a no-show report from your match partner for the 4 Vallées "
"Ambassadors Program.\n"
"\n"
"Your registration has been removed from the pool. If you believe this report "
"was made in error, please contact us for help.\n"
"\n"
"If you did not register for this programme, please ignore this email."
msgstr ""
"Nous avons reçu un signalement d'absence de la part de votre partenaire de "
"mise en relation pour le programme Ambassadeurs des 4 Vallées.\n"
"\n"
"Votre inscription a été retirée de la file. Si vous pensez que ce "
"signalement est erroné, contactez-nous pour obtenir de l'aide.\n"
"\n"
"Si vous ne vous êtes pas inscrit(e) à ce programme, ignorez cet e-mail."

#: public/views.py:144
msgid "Confirm your email to join the queue"
msgstr "Confirmez votre e-mail pour rejoindre la file d'attente"

#: public/views.py:146
#, python-format
